General.Name: Independent Film Development Corporation
General.Description: Independent Film Development Corporation operates in the hospitality division. The company operates a restaurant under Chef Eddie G's Kitchen name in East Harlem neighborhood in New York. It also owns distribution rights for various eclectic feature films; and episodic television programs, as well as for celebrity biography series worldwide. In addition, the company intends to acquire and manage real estate assets. Independent Film Development Corporation was founded in 2007 and is based in Irvine, California.
